						<summary>

						<p>This inscription is damaged at the end. It records a gift of money (<hi rend="italic">paḻañjalāgai</hi>) by Aḻagiyanāchchi āḻvi one of the ladies (<hi rend="italic">peṇḍugaḷ</hi>) of the palace establishment (<hi rend="italic">vēḷam</hi>). The money was deposited in the temple treasury of Tirumurugaṉ pūṇḍi Āḷuḍaiyanāyaṉār.</p>						

						</summary>
